ap;text-align:left;'></td><td style='white-space:nowrap;text-align:left;'></td><td style='white-space:nowrap;text-align:left;'>ON APPROACH, THE ENGINE WAS FOUND NOT TO RESPOND THE THROTTLE LEVER INPUT.  THE PILOT ENGAGED THE FUEL CONTROL MANUAL OVER-RIDE AND REGAINED AUTHORITY OVER THE ENGINE.  P&WC WILL MONITOR THE INVESTIGATION OF THE INCIDENT AND WILL ADVISE OF ROOT CAUSE ONCE ESTABLISHED.</td></tr>
