td style='white-space:nowrap;text-align:left;'></td><td style='white-space:nowrap;text-align:left;'></td><td style='white-space:nowrap;text-align:left;'></td><td style='white-space:nowrap;text-align:left;'></td><td style='white-space:nowrap;text-align:left;'>DURING CRUISE FLIGHT FROM SGF TO SUS AT 19000FT, THE AUTOPILOT MADE A SHARP UNCOMMAND PITCH UP.  THE PILOT DISCONNECTED THE A/P AND CONTINUED THE FLIGHT WITH A NORMAL APPROACH AND LANDING.</td></tr>
